<A>__{sounds of a train rolling to a halt, a shrill whistle.}
<L>__{exterior camp day}
<A>__{up on the door of a weathered cattle car as a german soldier steps into frame wearing that familiar gray of the all too familiar era. he throws the door to reveal a mass of huddled and frightened people inside. the words are not necessary. the language is not ours and the images say enough. men, women and children are herded off the train like cattle toward a large open yard. there they huddle until the germans begin to shout and shove through the mob.}
